comments: Weirdly felt like it could have been a bit more to it. The study felt a touch shallow.
fun survey! keep up the good work!

Ratings were difficult.  First rating -- top 7 or so, through taking out garbage, were for men.  Everything below that was for women so rank order was not accurate.  Hard to think about "agree" or "disagree" for more nuanced questions about male or female roles, it felt a bit too linear or not the right wording.
i was raised by a stay-at-home dad while my mother worked full time.
Just a note regarding my responses, overall think it's best for one parent (regardless if man or woman) to be a full time caregiver for children
